room_title: Escape room "Mad Hatter" by Eludesions Escape Rooms in Phoenix
room_address: 2710 W Bell Road, Suite 1200, Phoenix, AZ 85053
room_description: You have entered the world of Wonderland, where anything can happen - and oftentimes does! You can hear a party off in the distance. Perhaps the Mad Hatter can help you find your way home. Be aware of your surroundings - keeping your wits about you will be your most challenging task yet. Hurry, before you go completely mad!
